"ogimage":"http://s3-media1.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/oTdvClWEQqQ23FMDMVgHlw/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"I was astonished to not find this place on Yelp, as it is a place that I frequently visit. I could have sworn that I wrote a review about this place soon after it opened.  I wonder if I had just written the review in my mind or on paper, and then completely forgot to enter it.  What sets this place apart from other wine shops?  You get to try before you buy!  The website has a list of all the current wines they have to taste.  They also have a great schedule of tasting classes that you can take offered in French or English!  I have been to several of the tastings and enjoyed them all. They are very informative.  The owner is very knowledgeable and friendly.  They highlight wines from around the world, and the prices are affordable.  I love this little shop and the service is friendly.  Check out the website, sign up for their monthly newsletter, or like them on Facebook to keep posted on the rotating selection of wines here.",
